bio: Family of misfits trying to raise CHD Awareness. Also we make funny TikToks to pass the time. Check out the crazy with the link in our BIO.

social_posts.post_text: How is it I am married to the most handsome man & my best friend 😍🥰😘 #datenight was a success! #marriage #love

Finally getting to celebrate 8 years married to this dream boat! Massages & dinner with my best friend. I love you Bryan. The past 11 years with you have been the best of my life. Thank you for showing me true happiness & giving me the best two turds anyone could ask for! Happy Anniversary my love. ❤️ #anniversary #datenight #bestfriend #marriage

Our God Daughter is here! Lena Rosemarie we will love and spoil you for the rest of your life! And as your Fairy Godmother I will teach you in the ways of Target. Life’s truest blessing. 😂 BUT! What should my name be?!?!? I don’t know!!!! @pinkmermaid27 I love you! #baby #newborn
How wonderful life is now you’re in the world! My beautiful Goddaughter Lena Rosemarie ❤️ @pinkmermaid27 #godmother #baby #love
When life gives you a bald tire. Call your friend to pick you up from the shop and head to the park! 😉
The family is coming… ACT NORMAL! Kids: Absolutely not #family #crazy #kids

Never a dull moment in this house. Eleanor climbed on the counter and got the kitchen scissors. Gave herself a mullet! 🤦🏼‍♀️ Our amazing friend @ginaburba helped make the mullet even! Well… Baby Ray Cyrus refuses to do pigtails because “Wock & Wolllll!” Now all I see is @eltonjohn and once she heard him it was all over. She grabbed the piano and Piano Man will now live rent free in my head all day. At least she has good taste. Pray for me. The Lord is testing me and I did not study! This 3yo is WILD!!! Send help. #kids #kidsofinstagram #mullet

Mom & Dad had a much needed date night! TBH I didn’t feel like going, but he was so excited and researched @theporchpour and knew I would LOVE IT! I so did and now want to live there and the food was BEYOND incredible 😍😍😍 #datenight #marriage
When the food was too good & the kids were still at Nanny’s you go again for brunch! @theporchpour
How did it happen so fast?
A beautiful wedding with my beautiful butt nuggets #family #wedding

Wednesdays child is full of Woe! When she says, “Mom! I want all black! I’m Wednesday! I Gawofic!” Girl, bet. But if we’re doing this. We’re ALL IN! 😂 So this is apparently her first day of school outfit for first grade! #wednesday #goth

I will be your Pugsley any day Wednesday! First day of First grade is in the books for Lola. She was so excited to rock her new Goth threads, I dressed as Pugs and we danced to Goo Goo Muck from the car to the door of her classroom. I freaking love that she has no regard to look like everyone else or have a single fear what others would think. The only thing that bothered her was that I wouldn’t let her dye her hair black. 😂Stay weird kid, being a normie is boring! #firstdayofschool #wednesday
Be the change you wish to see in the world! Spent the day with @carterbloodcare & @lazorkophotography cannot wait to share with you all! #bethechange #giveback #chdawareness

I can’t even contain my excitement for my friend @turtlecreek.foodie! Darrens cookbook is out and it is not only BEAUTIFUL but each page has a QR code that directs you to the video. Listen some of you may know how to cook but the fact that I can watch a video too? Count me in! #cooking #food

Sent off mini @genesimmons to her first ever concert! And in true Catron style it was KISS! Rock & Roll all night baby! Cause in this house we party EVERY DAY! @kissonline (Don’t worry! We sent her packed with a letter to the paramedics if she has an episode & all the “Lola Essentials”) #kiss #kissarmy #chdawareness
35 never felt so… yea whatever growing up is for nerds! #birthday #momlife #millennials #35 #sleepover #party

We need to have a long talk with Waffle our elf! Apparently she spilled the beans that the girls wanted a dog so bad to Santa. Well… because a Great Pyrenees/Lab mix is too big to be on the sleigh they brought him early! So meet the newest member of the Catron family Puddin! ❤️
This top from @willowboutique has me singing Toxic and shouting “Its Britney Bitch”.
